      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model and contact formulation justified relative to expected material behavior and load regime.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening calibrated to coupon tensile data. Augmented Lagrangian contact formulation applied at screw-rod interface. Geometric nonlinearity enabled for large-displacement bending regime. Model form choices documented and peer-reviewed."
