      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test samples are production-representative with documented material certification and dimensional inspection.",
      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-lot hardware with full material certifications. CMM dimensional inspection confirmed all components within drawing tolerances. Sample selection covered two independent lots to capture inter-lot variability."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading scenarios or rationale provided for single-condition testing.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard configuration (5-degree lordotic angle, standard block spacing). Only one test condition was evaluated; variation in block spacing or lordotic angle was not explored. This factor falls below required level. The limitation is acknowledged; the single condition is considered representative of worst-case clinical loading for this device class per FDA guidance."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
