    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is mitigated by the conservative nature of the single ASTM F1717 configuration and FDA guidance alignment. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo propagation was completed and E/uval metrics satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds for all three QoIs. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support regulatory submission for this non-cannulated pedicle screw design.",
